niji resurs.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><i>NAI SARADNICI</i></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">Trenutno saraujemo i na listama smo sledeih finansijskih organizacija u Srbiji:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clear" style="text-align: left;"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clear" style="text-align: left;"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clear" style="text-align: left;"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="bd-row row-1 n-6 lv-1 row clearfix" style="text-align: left;">\r\n<div class="items-wrapper columns-inside row">\r\n<div class=" builder-column col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 four index-1 first ">\r\n<div class=" no-effect custom-settings settings-col has-custom alt-bg">\r\n<div class="items-wrapper items-inside index-1 first last">\r\n<div class="item-inner stpb-text">\r\n<div class="item-text-wrapper text-default no-effect">\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sberbank.rs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1025" src="http://www.datainvestment.rs/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/sarad_sberbank.png" alt="sarad_sberbank" width="280" height="80" /></a>\r\n<a href="http://www.societegenerale.rs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1026" src="http://www.datainvestment.rs/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/sarad_societe.png" alt="sarad_societe" width="240" height="70" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://www.erstebank.rs/rs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1026" src="http://www.datainvestment.rs/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Erste_Bank_Logo.svg_-e1448618926107.png" alt="sarad_erste" width="180" height="50" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://www.creditagricole.rs/pocetna.6.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1026" src="http://www.datainvestment.rs/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/credit-agricole-e1461838681151.png" alt="sarad_credit_agricole" width="200" height="50" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.kombank