vati da nas kontaktirate i uverite se u standarde kojima se rukovodimo i koji se mogu oekivati u naem odnosu prema radu.\r\nNai procenitelji su sertifikovani procenitelji od strane Ministarstva Pravde Republike Srbije, TEGOVA (the European group of valuers associations) i RICS (Royal Institution of Chartered Surveyors), iz razloga to elimo da stvorimo poverenje na finansijskom tritu.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="bd-row row-5 n-6 lv-1 last row clearfix">\r\n<div class="items-wrapper columns-inside row">\r\n<div class=" builder-column col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 four index-1 first ">\r\n<div class=" no-effect custom-settings settings-col has-custom alt-bg">\r\n<div class="items-wrapper items-inside index-1 first last">\r\n<div class="item-inner stpb-text">\r\n<div class="item-text-wrapper text-default no-effect">\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.mpravde.gov.rs/tekst/740/sudski-vestaci.php"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1019" src="http://www.datainvestment.rs/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/mpravde.png" alt="mpravde" width="180" height="90" /></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=" builder-column col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 four index-2">\r\n<div class=" no-effect custom-settings settings-col has-custom alt-bg">\r\n<div class="items-wrapper items-inside index-1 first last">\r\n<div class="item-inner stpb-text">\r\n<div class="item-text-wrapper text-default no-effect">\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.tegova.org/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1020" src="http://www.datainvestment.rs/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/tegova.png" alt="tegova" width="180" height="90" /></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=" builder-column col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 four index-3 last ">\r\n<div class=" no-effect custom-settings settings-col ha